request_0.formal_statement:
lemma isolate_variable:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x + 2/x = y + 2/y"
  shows "x - y = (2 * (x - y)) / (x * y)"

request_1.formal_statement:
lemma factor_expression:
  fixes a b :: real
  assumes "a - b = (c * (a - b)) / d"
  shows "d ≠ 0 ⟹ a - b ≠ 0 ⟹ 1 = c / d"

request_2.formal_statement:
lemma distinct_nonzero:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x ≠ 0" "y ≠ 0" "x ≠ y"
  shows "x * y ≠ 0"

request_3.formal_statement:
lemma manipulate_fractions:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x ≠ 0" "y ≠ 0"
  shows "x + 2/x = y + 2/y ⟷ (x - y) * xy = 2(x - y)"

request_4.formal_statement:
lemma divide_nonzero:
  fixes a b :: real
  assumes "a ≠ b"
  shows "a / (a - b) = 1"

request_5.formal_statement:
lemma product_relation:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x + 2/x = y + 2/y"
  shows "xy = 2"

request_6.formal_statement:
lemma rational_expression_manipulation:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x ≠ 0" "y ≠ 0" "x ≠ y"
  shows "x + 2/x = y + 2/y ⟷ (x - y)(xy - 2) = 0"

request_7.formal_statement:
lemma algebraic_manipulation:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x + 2/x = y + 2/y"
    and "x \<noteq> y"
  shows "x * y = 2"

request_8.formal_statement:
lemma common_denominator:
  fixes a b c d :: real
  assumes "b \<noteq> 0" "d \<noteq> 0"
  shows "(a/b) - (c/d) = (ad - bc) / (bd)"

request_9.formal_statement:
lemma distinct_elements:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x \<noteq> y"
  shows "x - y \<noteq> 0"

request_10.formal_statement:
lemma cross_multiplication:
  fixes x y :: real
  assumes "x + 2/x = y + 2/y"
    and "x \<noteq> 0" "y \<noteq> 0" "x \<noteq> y"
  shows "(x - y) * x * y = 2 * (x - y)"

request_11.formal_statement:
lemma non_zero_division:
  fixes a b :: real
  assumes "a \<noteq> b" "c \<noteq> 0"
  shows "a * c = b * c \<Longrightarrow> a = b"
